# azure-arc-gateway

This Terraform module deploys an Azure Arc Gateway and a do-no-delete lock on the resource.

## Input Variables

| Name                     | Type   | Description                                                             |
|--------------------------|--------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|
| arc_gateway_api_version  | string | Azure Arc Gateway Type API version                                      |
| arc_gateway_name         | string | Azure Arc Gateway Name                                                  |
| arc_gateway_type         | string | Azure Arc Gateway Type                                                  |
| resource_group_name      | string | Azure Resource Group Name                                               |

## Outputs

| Name                    | Description                              |
|-------------------------|------------------------------------------|
| arc_gateway_url         | The URL of the Azure Arc Gateway         |
| arc_gateway_resource_id | The resource ID of the Azure Arc Gateway |